  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2 \u0d85\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dba \u0db4\u0dd0\u0dc4\u0dd0\u0dbb \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1 \u0db4\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dab \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc5\u0db9 \u0d85\u0db4\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0db0 \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dca\u0da8\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dba",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Colombo Crime Division investigates the theft of the firearm",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to Police Media Spokesman Senior Superintendent of Police Advocate Nihal Talduwa, the Colombo Crime Division has handed over the investigation into the attack on an army soldier near Parliament and the kidnapping of his firearm and two magazines containing sixty bullets.",
        "The media spokesman said that on the advice of the Senior Deputy Inspector General of Western Province, Mr. Deshbandu Tennakoon, the investigation has been assigned to the Colombo Crime Division.",
        "During the protest held at Polduwa intersection, a soldier of the Wellawaya army camp who came for duty was beaten with an iron rod and this abduction was carried out.",
        "The seriously injured army soldiers are currently being treated at the army hospital",
        "The Police Media Spokesperson added that a special police team from the Colombo Crime Division has gone to the military hospital and obtained statements from the concerned army soldier."
      ],
